Firmware for the Motor Controller developed in-house
by Berkeley Pioneers in Engineering.

The following projects can be opened with the 
Arduino IDE available at "www.arduino.cc":

-- Basic firmware for the motor controller is under 
   the directory: "piemotorcontroller"

-- Firmware which blinks the status LEDs to confirm 
   that the microcontroller is working is under the  
   directory: "piemotorledblinker"